  <name>ColorMate</name>
  <summary>Your friendly color helper</summary>

  <description>
    <p>A color helper for web developers. Enter a color in #RGB, rgb() or hsl() and the corresponding representations with a handy copy button.</p>
  </description>

  <releases>
