      </description>
    </release>

    <release version="1.0.3" date="2021-09-12">
      <description>
        <p>This release introduces a new feature: you now can choose a color from the color chooser button and ColorMate will show you the corresponding representations.</p>
      </description>
    </release>

    <release version="1.0.2" date="2021-09-08">
      <description>
        <p>This release fixes some appdata issues</p>
      </description>
    </release>

    <release version="1.0.1" date="2021-09-08">
